(Translated by Google) Renovated tennis court

They ended up adding nets halfway up the fence to block the wind which is not high enough.

Plots 1 and 2 have a slope which is excessively inclined. Really for a patched ground not proud of the engineers.

Ils ont fini par rajouté des filets à demi hauteur de la clôture pour bloqué le vent ce qui n'est pas suffisamment haut.

(Translated by Google) There is a volleyball court but in the sand there are stones that can hurt easily if you jump hard (something common in volleyball jumping high)

In the end he said it was a joke and that it was to make people laugh
well joke bad taste and I wonder if there have been people who have already been fooled.

(Translated by Google) It is a park near my home. I go there regularly to play with my boy or just to walk. Several activities are available and during the summer the pool is very popular. However, the small children's park lacks entertainment in my opinion, I would add things to make them have fun, such as a small bridge. During the winter, I will slide and make snowmen! Unfortunately, I hardly see anyone during this winter season. Yet toddlers love to play in the snow!

(Original)
C'est un parc à proximité de chez moi.  J'y vais régulièrement jouer avec mon garçon ou simplement marcher. Plusieurs activités sont disponible et durant l'été la piscine est très apprécié. Cependant, le petit parc pour enfant manque de divertissements à mon avis , j'y rajouterais des trucs pour qu'ils s'amusent , exemple un petit pont. Durant l'hiver , je vais glisser et faire des bonhommes de neige! Malheureusement, je voit presque personne durant cette saison d'hiver. Pourtant les touts petits adorent jouer dans la neige!
